{"tid":278413,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"性格好毒既人入黎傾下計","createTime":"2017-06-10T12:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T17:07:16.000Z","uid":29487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72ef83f77115a167507150df30656d606b99ec79","tid":278413,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺自己係個好奇怪既人，<br />\n有時生活上遇到啲事情想同身邊人分享，但當同A講左一次我就唔會想同B再重覆咁講多次，<br />\n我覺得要講同一件事咁多次好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n例如同左朋友講，就會懶得同屋企人講；<br />\n同左A朋友講，就懶得同B朋友講。<br />\n所以我一直都無乜幾個知心朋友，<br />\n同唯一個幾個好朋友既相處模式我都慣左係咁。<br />\n但原來一路都係我單方面「慣」，<br />\n有啲朋友會覺得我忽視左佢地當佢地透明，<br />\n但我唔係想咁，<br />\n雖然唔係成日會同你分享野，<br />\n但你係我心目中個地位一直係好朋友無變過，只係懶得去溝通<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知有無人睇得明我想表達啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒撚格唔識表達<br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係我既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b21d6b7d6b9449ebb868541cdee44c4b7633dc1e","tid":278413,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:13:52.000Z","msg":"想報咩班"},{"pid":"4d76c369eb14bb4831fff936f4ad03919322ddf8","tid":278413,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:26:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想報咩班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做乜跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3fb2289e213ee55c3b8c26a1c4d7a8137c8e55","tid":278413,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想報咩班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做乜跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都話我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51965ec2fd0439de2bf74bb94b89a1a6ea56833","tid":278413,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:40:32.000Z","msg":"經常自己一個去睇戲，放假永遠唔會有人約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79555c4309edf542a1788c53284561f882e1a315","tid":278413,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T12:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99ba24b8b399abd90f9406ea7efb5590d31a7a8a","tid":278413,"uid":94679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔緊要啦    做自己最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb70d6b600b5d98c072ba0ebc833681e5490b72d","tid":278413,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想報咩班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做乜跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都話我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你幾時開班教煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa92ae7226f279c4a4b2563322f0af6bee87a84","tid":278413,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T13:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得女朋友，而無朋友，被朋友出賣過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我依家都係得返男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔緊要啦    做自己最開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係咁諗，但有時會覺得自己係咪太自我中心獨行獨斷，無理身邊人感受。不過講真我好enjoy自己一個人既時間"},{"pid":"0dfd745d4ada919d9c9796f1171c29e30c8b2c9a","tid":278413,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:32:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想報咩班</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你做乜跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都話我跟蹤佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你幾時開班教煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔識煮嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1ecd35defbe936d341edc5a8460e1769993194","tid":278413,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"其實毒撚一個更開心"},{"pid":"1d89a32849d2af769b0897ee672a1baeac4b947f","tid":278413,"uid":22444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:41:54.000Z","msg":"我唔鍾意同人講太多自己嘅嘢，人哋會覺得我好有距離感。<br />\n我覺得自己能力以內做到嘅嘢，就冇需要搵人幫手，麻煩到人，令到我慣咗自己一個做嘢嘅模式。<br />\n我比較鍾意自己一個人行街、睇戲、食飯、旅行，因為同朋友一齊，就要考慮對方嘅感受，遷就對方想做啲乜、食啲乜。一大班人嘅時候，要去邊度、食啲乜又要嘥時間諗一輪。<br />\n我都覺得自己好毒，但呢種生活模式令我感覺好舒服，所以我覺得冇乜問題。"},{"pid":"0611635ec35f012b9bf8a7fe8b0fe75a4a243dca","tid":278413,"uid":29487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T15:52:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔鍾意同人講太多自己嘅嘢，人哋會覺得我好有距離感。<br />\n我覺得自己能力以內做到嘅嘢，就冇需要搵人幫手，麻煩到人，令到我慣咗自己一個做嘢嘅模式。<br />\n我比較鍾意自己一個人行街、睇戲、食飯、旅行，因為同朋友一齊，就要考慮對方嘅感受，遷就對方想做啲乜、食啲乜。一大班人嘅時候，要去邊度、食啲乜又要嘥時間諗一輪。<br />\n我都覺得自己好毒，但呢種生活模式令我感覺好舒服，所以我覺得冇乜問題。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTotally agree<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我過得好自在  但咁令到朋友唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e288be5dddf16b9d7c7c0b7827615c6f1dd27542","tid":278413,"uid":68255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"我反而係會想搵多幾個人聽 比意見我<br />\n我好想人地聽我講自己d野 但係又怕人地覺得我煩 所以好難搵對象<br />\n如果講到一半佢眉頭額角表示出佢無興趣聽既話我就輕輕帶過就算"},{"pid":"2190395ca0c202ad4e8309452f266c30909e9941","tid":278413,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n唔識同人傾計<br />\n典型話題終結者<br />\n所以就黎24都仲係a0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3200165bae3c240008ca4d69a959e1774246ce72","tid":278413,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"明白 同樓主一樣<br />\n覺得自己講完既句字再重新組織講多次好麻煩<br />\n我本身係個表達能力差內向既人<br />\n好多事都覺得冇咩必要同其他人分享<br />\n會覺得自己既呢d事根本冇人想知"}]}